<scriptment id="84000" point="new_offer" localizationstatus="original" fictionaldate="2011-11-04" status="final">
	<part>
		<narration>Soleil sits alone in the bar. Someone stands before her.</narration>
		<line id="1000" speaker="someone" voicelang="en">Greetings, Madame Soleil.</line>
		<line id="2000" speaker="yuki" voicelang="en">What?</line>
		<line id="3000" speaker="someone" voicelang="en">I've from afar observed the Sega Corporation's financial data.</line>
		<line id="4000" speaker="someone" voicelang="en">The future is bleak for the New Parisian-Nagoyan Network.</line>
		<narration>Soleil glares at her.</narration>
		<line id="5000" speaker="yuki" voicelang="en">What are you supposed to be, The Group's "good cop?"</line>
		<line id="6000" speaker="someone" voicelang="en">I am from neither side nor a neutral party.</line>
		<line id="7000" speaker="someone" voicelang="en">I work for the benefit of the medium.</line>
		<line id="8000" speaker="someone" voicelang="en">I will offer Sega confidential protection under the umbrella of my organization.</line>
		<line id="9000" speaker="someone" voicelang="en">We're international, we're surreptitiously powerful, and we're universal.</line>
		<line id="10000" speaker="someone" voicelang="en">At the snap of your fingers you will gain trillions attributed to "inexplicable fortune."</line>
		<line id="11000" speaker="someone" voicelang="en">The New PNN may live on.</line>
		<line id="12000" speaker="yuki" voicelang="en">The New PNN would be no better than The Group.</line>
		<line id="13000" speaker="someone" voicelang="en">I feared and awaited such a response. Men of honor never last.</line>
		<narration>She puts down her card.</narration>
		<line id="14000" speaker="someone" voicelang="en">Sanchez.</line>
		<line id="15000" speaker="someone" voicelang="en">Call me when you change your mind.</line>
	</part>
</scriptment>